  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators plan to develop and test an intervention using peer specialists (Veterans
      who have managed PTSD and completed PE) to provide support services for Veterans using
      prolonged exposure therapy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators will use qualitative data from Veterans and PE providers to revise the
      investigators' manualized intervention for peer support services, then complete a feasibility
      trial to assess the feasibility and acceptability of Peer Enhanced Prolonged Exposure
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
